headline: Altria Picked by UBS as Safe Haven Dividend Stock
summary: Altria Group, Inc. (NYSE:MO) is one of the best stocks for a retirement stock portfolio. The stock was highlighted by UBS equity strategists as one of the companies that offer “safe haven” qualities, marked by strong operational performance, low stock price volatility, and a substantial dividend.
